subtitle.zh: Rspack & webpack 构建分析工具

toolStackDesc.en: High-performance toolchain built around Rspack to boost modern web development
toolStackDesc.zh: 围绕 Rspack 打造的高性能工具链，助力现代 Web 开发

frameworkAgnosticDesc.en: Rsdoctor support all projects built on Rspack or webpack.
frameworkAgnosticDesc.zh: Rsdoctor 支持分析用 Rspack 和 webpack 构建的项目。

buildTimeDesc.en: To display the compile execution time and process in the form of a timing diagram.
buildTimeDesc.zh: 以时序图的形式显示编译执行时间和过程。

buildActionsDesc.en: Visually view the compilation changes of each file in each loader.
buildActionsDesc.zh: 可视化的查看每个 loader 对每个文件的编译更改。

bundleAnalysisDesc.en: Visually view the bundles & modules relationship, module reference relationship and repeated packages in detail.
bundleAnalysisDesc.zh: 直观地详细查看 Bundle 和模块关系、模块引用关系和重复包等产物详情。

bundleDiffDesc.en: Through comparison, the deterioration and change of the product are found.
bundleDiffDesc.zh: 通过对比发现产物劣化及变动。

buildScanDesc.en: Built-in build rule scanning, and also supports custom rules.
buildScanDesc.zh: 内置构建规则扫描，同时支持自定义规则。
